    scene jazz2 with dissolve
    laura "Is that her?"
    bffmom "Yes, that's Vanessa."
    bff "Isn't she cool? [name] is so lucky."
    bffmom "And you aren't?"
    bff "Uhh..."
    pause 1.0
    scene jazz4 with dissolve
    "While the room settles, [stepmom_name] leans into the mic."
    smom "Good evening... Brightmoor."
    mc "(Oh here we go.)"
    pause 0.5
    "The band eases in, soft and deliberate."
