    scene bffsisproblem5 with dissolve
    bffmom "So what did she find out about that place?"
    bffsis "Not much, she doesn't really want to talk about it."
    if emmaasked:
        scene bffsisproblem6 with dissolve
        mc "Yeah, she didn't say much to me about it either."
        mc "She did show me a burnt piece of paper though, the kind Justin was always talking about when he was working night shifts there."
        mc "Some strange rules he was supposed to follow, and they would change every day."
        mc "The whole thing was... creepy."
    scene bffsisproblem7 with dissolve
    bffmom "I don't know, all of this sounds very ominous guys."
    scene bffsisproblem5 with dissolve
    bffmom "Bridgette, what are you not telling us? What was it about Justin?"
    scene bffsisproblem4 with dissolve
    bffsis "Emma is obsessed with that place, and we kept telling her not to go alone but..."
    scene bffsisproblem3 with dissolve
    bffsis "She insisted."
    bffsis "And before I knew it, I had agreed to go with her."
    scene bffsisproblem4 with dissolve
    bffsis "And what we saw... It was as if-"
    scene bffsisproblem3 with dissolve
    bffsis "As if..."
    bffmom "As if... What, honey?"
    scene bffsisproblem2 with dissolve
    bffsis "As if it did not want us living." with vpunch
    mc "Wow, that seems a bit much."
    scene bffsisproblem1 with dissolve
    bffsis "You don't understand!"
    scene bffsisproblem3 with dissolve
    bffsis "We felt watched the entire time we were there, and when we went inside..."
    bffsis "There was nobody there, but then..."
    scene bffsisproblem4 with dissolve
    bffsis "Emma's phone was recording, and it picked up an EVP."
    scene bffsisproblem5 with dissolve
    bffmom "What's an EVP?"
    scene bffsisproblem6 with dissolve
    mc "It's an abbreviation, it stands for 'Electronic Voice Phenomenon'"
    mc "It's what they call it when they think they've caught an audio recording of ghosts and the likes."
    scene bffsisproblem8 with dissolve
    bffsis "Yes! How do you know all that?"
    mc "It's... a long story."
    mc "But anyway, about this EVP?"
    scene bffsisproblem9 with dissolve
    bffsis "I had Tim run it through some audio programs and it's Justin's voice, clear as day!"
    mc "Really? How is that possible?"
    mc "(I mean, I guess we never did find his actual body but what are the chances?)"
    scene bffsisproblem10 with dissolve
    bffsis "Look, I know it sounds crazy but you have to trust me. It's Justin."
    mc "Then we must go there at once."
    scene bffsisproblem8 with dissolve
    bffmom "Are you sure, [name]?"
    bffmom "I mean, none of this screams 'good idea' to me."
    mc "Agreed, but if there is even a small chance of finding more information about him, or what happened to him, I'm taking it."
    scene bffsisproblem9 with dissolve
    bffsis "How about we meet there later? I'll bring Emma too."
    menu:
        "Agree.":
            mc "Sounds good to me."
            $ questlog.StartQuest(quest_bridgettebreakdown)
            scene bffsisproblem10 with dissolve
            bffsis "Okay, thanks [name]."
            $ bffsislove += 10
            scene black with slow_fade
            bffmom "I don't know guys, why don't you-"
            bffsis "No mom! We're going!"
            mc "(I didn't know Bridgette cared this much about him, maybe I underestimated her.)"
            pause 1.0
            return
        "Maybe later.":
            $ bridgettebreakdown_seen = True
            scene bffsisproblem8 with dissolve
            mc "I'll think about it."
            bffsis "Alright [name], I hope I can count on you for this."
            bffmom "Either way, you guys better watch out. It's a dangerous world out there!"
            mc "Of course, Naomi."
            return

label cuckoofinale:
    scene black with fade
    "Upon arriving at Tim's place to help him out, you hear yelling coming from his room."
    scene cuckootim with dissolve
    bffex "Oh my god Tim! So now you actually called your friend over to save your sorry ass?!"
    bffex "I've been stuck here, naked and humiliated for an hour, while you flailed around like a virgin on prom night."
    bffex "You are such a pathetic loser!"
    bff "Riley, please calm down..."
    scene cuckootim2 with dissolve
    bffex "What's next, Tim? Gonna call your mom to help too? Or are you saving that for when you finally figure out how sex works?"
    bffex "You could've at least read the manual on these things!"
    bff "There actually is no manual, you use a magic word."
    bffex "Unbelievable... a magic word..."
    "It seems like a heated argument, you arrive just in time."
    mc "Uhh, guys?"
    scene cuckootim3 with dissolve
    bff "Ahh, hey [name]."
    bff "The cuffs you gave me are broken."
    bff "We can't get them off."
    mc "I tried to tell you..."
    mc "It's a gag gift, it was never meant to be used seriously."
    bffex "What?!"
    mc "I mean, he was so excited he didn't want to listen and before I could explain..."
    bffex "Great, just great."
    scene cuckootim4 with dissolve
    mc "Here let me get you out of these."
    "You walk over to Riley while the two of them continue arguing."
    bffex "Don't you dare touch me!"
    bff "Riley, I..."
    bffex "Just leave me alone Tim!"
    bffex "This is all your fault!"
    bffex "You're a joke!"
    mc "(This is getting out of hand...)"
    mc "So, you're supposed to say a safe word and they're supposed to open."
    mc "But during the demonstration, it didn't work so well..."
    mc "They ended up stuck like this."
    mc "Until a random passerby was reading 'Tofu' off their grocery list."
    pause 0.3
    "The cuffs click open."
    scene cuckootim5 with dissolve
    bff "Tofu?"
    bffex "Ugh, finally..."
    bffex "Thank you [name]."
    $ bffexlove += 5
    bffex "If it wasn't for you, I would still be stuck like this."
    bffex "Imagine the embarrassment..."
    mc "No problem."
    scene cuckootim6 with dissolve
    "Riley gets dressed quickly and glares at Tim as she walks out the door."
    bff "So... Riley I was thinking about next time we could perhaps-"
    bffex "Next time?!"
    bffex "Enjoy your hand, since that's the only thing you'll ever satisfy."
    "She slams the door with all her strength."
    pause 0.5
    scene cuckootim7 with dissolve
    bff "Well..."
    bff "That could've gone better..."
    bff "Could've gone worse too, I guess..."
    mc "(Poor guy...)"
    mc "(He was so excited about trying them out too...)"
    $ questlog.EndQuest(quest_cuckoofinale)
    mc "Don't worry about her, Tim."
    mc "I'm sure you'll find someone better."
    mc "(Hopefully someone who has lots of patience...)"
    $ havemet_bffex = True
    return

label timplan2:
    scene naomitim_idle with dissolve
    mc "I guess we're going to leak the research."
    scene timchoice with dissolve
    $ bfflove += 5
    $ bffmomlove -= 5
    bff "Right up my alley, dude!"
    bffmom "You two better know what you're doing."
    bffmom "This isn't a game!"
    scene timdialogue2 with dissolve
    bff "Leave it to me [name], just give me the research and go home."
    scene timdialogue4 with dissolve
    bff "I'll call you when it's done."
