                    mc "...Yes?"
                    scene timdialogue2 with dissolve
                    bff "She does check in on her every once in a while, without her knowing about it."
                    mc "Like how?"
                    bff "Like going to school but then never entering her office."
                    bff "Or she'll go to her house just to check on her, but never actually visit her."
                    mc "Hmmm..."
                    mc "(That's... awfully secretive?)"
                    mc "Why would she do that if she doesn't want to have anything to do with Mrs. Brown?"
                    scene timdialogue1 with dissolve
                    bff "As I said, I don't know bro."
                    bff "She doesn't know that I know."
                    scene timdialogue3 with dissolve
                    bff "But when I started going to school there, I started getting to know my aunt better and mom didn't like it."
                    mc "Hmmm, that seems out of character for Naomi..."
                    mc "Now I'm really curious as to what's going on between them."
                    scene timdialogue1 with dissolve
                    bff "Yeah bro, if you ask me..."
