            scene teachshoot5 with dissolve
            mathteach "So how did I do?"
            photolady "Incredible, Felicia will be pleased."
            mc "(So am I...)"
            scene teachshoot6 with dissolve
            mathteach "Did you like it too, [name]?"
            mc "Me? I uh, yeah.. A lot!"
            "She looks visibly amused by your answer as she leaves the room to change."
            scene studio8 with dissolve
            photolady "She did it!"
            mc "Yeah, she did."
            scene studio7 with dissolve
            photolady "I'm sure Felicia will be impressed."
            photolady "And you probably landed yourself a sweet little side gig."
