    scene roberttalk02 with dissolve
    rob "I'm afraid I don't have any cuckoo cuffs in stock right now, sir."
    rob "They sold out pretty quickly."
    rob "Officer Sadie who came over to assist during the demonstration actually bought the last six pairs I had."
    mc "Well, can't you order some more?"
    scene roberttalk03 with dissolve
    rob "The problem is, after the fiasco the other day during the demonstration..."
    rob "People started ditching them left and right."
    mc "(Jeez, I wonder why...)"
    scene roberttalk01 with dissolve
    rob "I can't justify ordering more stock if no one is buying them."
