    scene fabiennedialogue2 with vpunch
    lady "OhŌĆö!"  
    pause 0.5
    scene fabiennedialogue3 with dissolve
    lady "Well nowŌĆ” aren't you full of surprises?"
    mc "You're not mad?"
    scene fabiennedialogue4 with dissolve
    lady "Please. You think I haven't seen worse in these changing rooms?"  
    lady "But you do look a little... full."
    "She steps closer, eyes flicking downward as she lightly runs a finger across your chest."
    lady "What if I make you nut right here, in the middle of the store?"
    mc "(God...)"
    "Before you can react, the store bell chimes."
