        mc "So why are you telling me this?"
        brenda "Maybe we can help each other."
        brenda "But before I tell you more, I need to know if you are serious about this."
        mc "I am serious about this."
        scene meetbrenda04 with dissolve
        brenda "Alright, then listen carefully."
        brenda "I have a plan, but I want you to show me that you are serious about this."
        brenda "I need more evidence about my husband before I can take him down."
        brenda "You mentioned your friend Elke, if she can be convinced to give you the files then great."
        scene meetbrenda05 with dissolve
        brenda "But if not, I need something else."
        brenda "A backup plan if you will."
        mc "What do you need?"
        brenda "I need you to get in touch with the hooker that my husband is seeing."
        mc "A hooker...?"
        mc "I don't know..."
        scene meetbrenda04 with dissolve
        brenda "Listen [name], I know this is a lot to ask."
        brenda "But if you can get me more proof from her, then I have all I need to take him and claire down for good."
        mc "(Ugh...)"
        mc "Fine, I'll try and get a rendezvous with her."
        scene meetbrenda05 with dissolve
        brenda "Thank you [name]."
        $ questlog.EndQuest(quest_brendameeting, calendar.day)
        $ questlog.StartQuest(quest_brendatest)
        return
    elif quest_meetbrenda in questlog.quest_list:
        $ meet_character("havemet_brenda", "images/mayorshouse/Brendameet.webm", 3.0)
        scene meetbrenda01
        "You arrive at the mayor's house and find Mrs. Winfield waiting for you at the porch."
        brenda "Hello [name], thank you for coming."
        mc "Hello Mrs. Winfield."
        mc "You wanted to talk to me?"
        if mayorblackmailed:
            scene meetbrenda02 with dissolve
            brenda "My husband told me about your little stunt."
            brenda "Lingerie, really? BoldŌĆ” or foolish."
            brenda "Now, let's talk about what you're going to do for me."
        else:
            scene meetbrenda02 with dissolve
            brenda "Yes, my husband told me about you."
            brenda "He said you were quite..."
            brenda "resourceful."
            mc "I try my best."
        scene meetbrenda01 with dissolve
        brenda "I have a small favor to ask of you."
        mc "What is it?"
        scene meetbrenda03 with dissolve
        brenda "I have been suspecting my husband is caught up in some shady business."
        mc "I mean... I've had one meeting with him, and I already know he is."
        scene meetbrenda02 with dissolve
        brenda "I know, but this is different."
        mc "How so?"
        scene meetbrenda03 with dissolve
        brenda "Call it a feeling."
        mc "I see."
        scene meetbrenda04 with dissolve
        brenda "I need you to find out what he is up to."
        mc "How am I supposed to do that?"
        brenda "He has a meeting with some people on Thursday at 16:00."
        brenda "I need you to be there and find out what they are talking about."
        brenda "Bonus points if you manage to plant a bug in his office."
        mc "A bug?"
        scene meetbrenda05 with dissolve
        brenda "Don't worry, I'll provide you one."
        mc "Fine, I can do that."
        brenda "Find out what they are up to, and give me a call."
        mc "And... In return?"
        scene meetbrenda04 with dissolve
        brenda "What do you want?"
        mc "I too have a favor to ask."
        brenda "What is it?"
        mc "I need you to convince your husband to retract the permit for the coffeeshop."
        scene meetbrenda05 with dissolve
        brenda "That's it?"
        mc "Yes."
        brenda "Fine, I can do that."
        brenda "You get me the information I need, and I'll get you what you want."
        mc "Consider it done."
        "With that, you take your leave."
        $ bag.add_item(bug)
        $ questlog.EndQuest(quest_meetbrenda, calendar.day)
        $ questlog.StartQuest(quest_mayormeeting)
        return
    elif quest_mayormeeting3 in questlog.quest_list:
        "You arrive at the mayor's house and find Mrs. Winfield waiting for you at the porch."
        scene meetbrenda01 with dissolve
        brenda "Hello [name], thank you for coming."
        mc "Hello Mrs. Winfield."
        brenda "So what have you found out?"
        mc "Well I was a bit shocked to find out that your husband is involved in some shady business..."
        mc "With my boss."
        scene meetbrenda02 with dissolve
        brenda "Your boss?!"
        mc "Yes, Mr. Dictonic."
        mc "They were talking about some new drug they are making."
        mc "Vitalis"
        scene meetbrenda03 with dissolve
        brenda "Vitalis?"
        brenda "Never heard of it."
        mc "Well, they were talking about how it is going to be a game changer."
        mc "My boss gave your husband a sample to test."
        scene meetbrenda02 with dissolve
        brenda "A sample?!"
        brenda "He's going to test it himself??"
