        mc "And then..."
        brenda "And then what?"
        mc "I'll show you."
        "You take out your phone and show her the video of the mayor after he took the drug."
        scene meetbrenda04 with dissolve
        brenda "Thank you [name]."
        brenda "This is exactly what I needed."
        mc "Wait, you're not shocked at all?"
        scene meetbrenda05 with dissolve
        brenda "No, not really."
        brenda "I had my suspicions."
        mc "So you knew he was up to no good?"
        scene meetbrenda04 with dissolve
        brenda "[name], he hasn't been able to get it up for years."
        mc "(jeez...)"
        brenda "At least now I have a reason to have my own fun."
        scene meetbrenda05 with dissolve
        brenda "All this time, I thought I was the unfaithful one."
        brenda "But here he is, the second he can get it up, he is out there with some hooker."
        mc "Wait, what about our deal?"
        brenda "Don't worry, I will talk to him about the coffeeshop."
        brenda "I will make sure he retracts the permit."
        mc "Thank you Mrs. Winfield."
        brenda "No, thank you [name]."
        brenda "I will call you later this week to let you know when he has retracted the permit."
        mc "Alright, I will be waiting for your call."
        "With that, you take your leave."
        $ brendalove += 5
