                smom "So, I was wondering if you know of any places that are hiring?"
                mc "Oh, uhm... There is the new coffeeshop that opened up near the school."
                scene shomedad06 with dissolve
                smom "Oh, that's a great idea!"
                dad "A coffeeshop?"
                mc "Yeah, it's pretty modern and getting popular."
                mc "Half the school goes there after classes."
                smom "Oh, that sounds perfect!"
