    scene maysneak15 with vpunch
    mc "Oh god, oh god!! *thud* AHH!!!"
    loudmom "Oh my-"
    loudmom "Oh my god!! HAH!"
    scene maysneak16 with dissolve
    "Just as you finish, and catch your breath in your uncomfortable, dark and undeniably difficult situation down there..."
    loudmom "You made quite a mess there sugar!"
    loudmom "My daddy used to say 'You can't do real work without gettin dirty!'"
    loudmom "I guess he was right."
    loudmom "Let me clean you up real good!"
    mc "No wait! WAIT!!"
    scene maysneak17 with dissolve
    "It's too late, May turns on the ice cold water."
    mc "AHHH S-s-"
    mc "STOP!! GOD!!!"
    loudmom "Hahaha! Learned your lesson yet?"
    mc "Y-yes yes!!!"
    scene maysneak18 with dissolve
    "After a solid 5 minutes, you manage to crawl out from underneath May's sink with your cock still dangling out of your pants."
    "May can't contain her laughter, as she is standing there cackling through the whole ordeal."
    mc "Yeah, yeah... You had your fun."
    mc "Listen uhh... Any chance we can keep this between us?"
    loudmom "Hahah, no chance sugar!"
    loudmom "But you should get out of here before the neighbours come asking me to send you over there too."
    mc "(I'm not gonna live this one down anytime soon, am I?)"
    $ calendar.addtime(20)
    return

label homelessdialogue:
    scene homelesstrailer1 with dissolve
    if homelessencounter_seen:
        homeless "ŌĆ”Been thinkin' about what I told you. About Joyce. Some days I wish I'd kept my mouth shutŌĆ” other days I'm glad someone finally heard it."
        homeless "ŌĆ”Didn't mean to dump all that on you, kid."
        menu:
            "I'm glad you told me.":
                mc "Brightmoor needs people like you to speak up and tell your story if we want this madness to ever end."
