        mayor "Ohh yeah! I can practically feel it surging through my dick."
        mayor "I haven't been this hard, even in my prime."
        mayor "Are you ready darling?"
        mayor "You better be, daddy is hungry. Ghehe!"
        boss "Let's begin."
